WEBVTT

00:03:29.523 --> 00:03:33.605
Tassavur qiling, kimdur asl kemaning 
har bir almashtirilgan qismlarini yig'ib,

00:03:33.605 --> 00:03:38.744
asl kemani to'liqligicha qayta tiklasa?

00:03:38.744 --> 00:03:43.783
Qayta tiklangan kema qurib bitkazilganda, 
ikkita kema paydo bo'ladi:

00:03:43.783 --> 00:03:45.798
biri Afina sohilida,

00:03:45.798 --> 00:03:48.242
ikkinchisi esa kimningdir hovlisida.
Va ularning

00:03:48.242 --> 00:03:50.875
har biri "Tesey Kemasi" 
deb nomlanish huquqiga ega.

00:03:50.875 --> 00:03:51.875
Ammo ulardan faqat

00:03:51.875 --> 00:03:55.085
bittasi haqiqiydir.
Xo'sh, qaysi biri?

00:03:55.085 --> 00:03:56.374
To'g'rirog'i, buni shaxsan

00:03:56.374 --> 00:03:59.583
sizga qanday aloqasi bor?
"Tesus Kemasi" kabi, siz doimo

00:03:59.583 --> 00:04:01.727
sodir bo'ladigan o'zgarishlar to'plamisiz: